   However, on the day Waltzer said he showed up, the couple made an
appearence on ABC's ``20-20'' in which Givens called Tyson a
manic-depressive with ``an extremely volatile temper.'' The boxer
later reportedly flew into a rage, and the couple sued each other
for divorce in October.
   Waltzer said he still is waiting for the check and wants payment,
with interest, plus court costs and legal fees.
   Efforts to reach Tyson for comment were unsuccessful. Calls to
his home went unanswered.
