<HEAD>Arson Destroys Nine Homes In New Orleans' Mid-City</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NEW ORLEANS (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A suspicious fire destroyed almost an entire
block of an inner city neighborhood Thursday night, but no one was
injured and the blaze was brought under control within an hour,
officials said.
   The fire was set in a vacant building and quickly spread. Nine
buildings were destroyed, but only one was occupied at the time,
