<2ND_LINE>PM-Wall Street 3pm,0412</2ND_LINE>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The stock market drifted mostly lower today in
subdued trading as investors awaited new evidence on the strength of
the economy.
   The Dow Jones average of 30 industrial stocks, up 12.98 points on
Wednesday and nearly 40 points over the past three sessions, was
