<DATELINE>BATTLE CREEK, Mich. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Horst W. Schroeder was named Thursday
as president and chief operating officer of Kellogg Co., the cereal
maker said.
   Kellogg is the world's leading maker of ready-to-eat breakfast
cereals.
   Also on Thursday, Dr. Gary E. Costley was named president of
