has served since 1986 as executive vice president, president of U.S.
subsidiaries, and chairman and chief executive officer of Mrs.
Smith's Frozen Foods Co.
   Elliott joined Kellogg last year after 30 years with the Price
Waterhouse accounting company. Kellogg had been one of his major
clients.
